README

# -------------------------------
# Overview
# -------------------------------

The Finatra framework uses the slf4j-api for logging. By coupling the framework to only slf4j, application developers
can choose the logging implementation. inject-slf4j adds slf4j bridges for the following logging providers:

  * log4j
  * java-util-logging,
  * commons-logging

Note: the above bridges are only installed if the slf4j-jdk14 logging implementation is not on the classpath.

See http://twitter.github.io/finatra/user-guide/logging/ for more information.